com.skratchdot.riff.wav
Interface CuePoint

All Known Implementing Classes:
CuePointImpl
public interface CuePoint

A representation of the model object 'Cue Point'.

The following features are supported:

  • Cue Point ID
  • Position
  • Data Chunk ID
  • Chunk Start
  • Block Start
  • Sample Offset

See Also:
WavPackage.getCuePoint()
